Simulation

Class Station

  • java.lang.Object
    • Simulation.Location
      • Simulation.Station

  • public class Station
extends Location
    A class representing a bus station. Passengers start randomly distributed among the stations and are only removed from the simulation once they arrive at their station of choice.
    Author:
    Eliot J. Kaplan

    • Method Detail

      • manhattanDistance

        public int manhattanDistance(Station other)
        Determines the manhattan distance from this station to another one. Because busses move one space per timestep, it will take this many steps to get from this station to the other one.
        Parameters:
        other - The station to measure distance to
        Returns:
        the manhattan distance from this station to other.
